      "role": "user",
      "content": "i guess. but it feels different than just being bored or looking for a new hobby. it’s more like... the trip is naturally coming to an end. you reach the final stop, you turn in your tickets, and you just leave the station. everything feels so heavy and finished. it’s like i’m just waiting for the last flight to depart.",
